Class declaration

  Declare method (parameters are a company array and the desired id, an int)(return an int)

    Declare and initialize value to be returned (-1)
    
    For loop looks through each object in array
      For each iteration, use getID method for the array object and save the returned id in a variable
      Use if statement to compare desired id to id obtained in the iteration. 
        If they match, return the location of the Company array object
        If they don't, the loop moves onto the next iteration
    End for loop
    
    If a match is not found, -1 is returned
  End of find method
End of class
